text: Jacques Pourtau (born 12 November 1935) is a French wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman lightweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:French male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of France Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Landes (department)
